column2: RETURNING TO POST C CLEAN 2 FULL SECTIONS OF WINDOWS. 32 FT LADDER WORK.

WE RAN OUT OF WINSOL HARD WATER REMOVER. IT IS NECESSARY FOR THE HARD WATER TO COME OFF, A1 DOES NOT WORK. CLEANED 5 WINDOWS APPROX. STARTED ON THE INTERNATIONAL ROAD SIDE. ROB AND I HAD THE ONES HE WANTED CLEANED MARKED INSIDE WITH TAPE, BUT APPARENTLY HE HAS TO TAKE THAT OFF OVER THE WEEKEND, SO CALL ROB TO SEE WHICH ONES TO CLEAN. ALSO CALL ROHAN FOR ASSISTANCE.
